import React from 'react'
import {
	Box,
	Center,
	FormControl,
	FormLabel,
	FormErrorMessage,
	FormHelperText,
	Input
} from '@chakra-ui/react';

const RegisterPage = () => {
	return (
		<Center>
			<Box>
				<FormControl id='login' isRequired>
					<FormLabel>Login</FormLabel>
					<Input type='login'/>
				</FormControl>
				<FormControl id='password' isRequired>
					<FormLabel>Password</FormLabel>
					<Input type='password'/>
					<FormHelperText>Remember to never share your password with anybody</FormHelperText>
				</FormControl>
			</Box>
		</Center>
	)
}

export default RegisterPage;
